{"tid":1665754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[立flag] 火魔法師入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-20T16:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T14:28:43.000Z","uid":83648,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"124f36a9bbf93c7997b1dddb594d478c8012c835","tid":1665754,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"今日窩打老道個火係正民居下面<br />\n而個民居外牆就係一個竹棚<br />\n你一陣大風啲座大廈就𤏸撚晒<br />\n仲有你睇下啲煙<br />\n焗都焗死啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ChPDg2H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChPDg2H.png&h=d26579bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0Pf3HN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0Pf3HN.png&h=c8a2a322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外舖入面都好撚危險<br />\n你控制唔撚到<br />\n燒到樓上就又係仆街<br />\n真係好大機會傷及市民<br />\n係成個抗爭立即收皮<br />\n<br />\n以為咪撚舖內玩<br />\n同埋火欄盡量遠啲"},{"pid":"20a2ac24eca0326653cf457435fbe8e6816356d7","tid":1665754,"uid":228437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母有紋身手足全部同我入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665753</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab3422890be1dc0650827eb10f18f73bf039d7a4","tid":1665754,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"有用 <br />\n下次改進"},{"pid":"223c19311b977b75ec15e5df44d7f03c6c0b6974","tid":1665754,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"6cb140d9d81d8351607897332d1ead0470bfad9c","tid":1665754,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"de957fa9be6750f73c118e67159bdc955c9181c4","tid":1665754,"uid":323908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0088f084c53004cbb4a899e608f680507dcdd8a","tid":1665754,"uid":83648,"like":0